# {{military}} Delinquent in Qualifications. A term used on United States submarines and Naval Nuclear Power Program to refer to being behind the "curve" (a requisite amount of forward progress in one's qualifications).
#:* John is so dinq that he could get 100 signatures a day and he'd still be behind.